Class ConsoleColours

java.lang.Object
capstone.Extras.ConsoleColours
public final class ConsoleColours extends Object
ConsoleColours which are to be used in the Teller App. Adapted from https://stackoverflow.com/questions/5762491/how-to-print-color-in-console-using-system-out-println.
